GitClone_key1: Aapke aur aapke peers ki stories (puri nahi bas beginnings), ab github pe hai - jahan se aap sab ek doosre ki stories dekh sakte hain aur collaborate kar sakte hain.
GitClone_key2: GitHub se apne peer ki story apne system mein copy karne ke liye hum "git clone" command ka use karte hain.
GitClone_key3: Iss link ke through "git clone" command ka use dekhiye.
GitClone_key5: Apne peers ki stories "git clone" use karke apne system mein copy kijiye.
